%20by%20Pracheen%20Shiv%20Mandir%20Avam%20Akhada%20Samiti%20seeking%20quashing%20and%20setting%20aside%20the%20order%20of%20demolition%20given%20for%20the%20Pracheen%20Shiv%20Mandir%2C%20situated%20near%20Taj%20Enclave%2C%20Geeta%20Colony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLord%20Shiva%20does%20not%20need%20our%20protection%3B%20rather%2C%20we%2C%20the%20people%2C%20seek%20his%20protection%20and%20blessings%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Dharmesh%20Sharma%20said%20in%20the%20judgement%20passed%20on%20May%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20there%20could%20be%20no%20iota%20of%20doubt%20that%20Lord%20Shiva%20would%20be%20happier%20if%20the%20Yamuna%20riverbed%20and%20the%20floodplains%20are%20cleared%20of%20all%20encroachments%20and%20unauthorised%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20half-hearted%20plea%20by%20the%20learned%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioner%20that%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20being%20the%20deity%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20must%20be%20also%20impleaded%20in%20the%20present%20matter%20is%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20give%20an%20altogether%20different%20colour%20to%20the%20entire%20dispute%20to%20sub-serve%20the%20vested%20interest%20of%20its%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Sharma%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20it%20is%20borne%20from%20the%20face%20of%20the%20record%20that%20the%20petitioner%20society%2C%20which%20was%20registered%20in%202018%2C%20has%20miserably%20failed%20to%20place%20on%20record%20any%20documents%20with%20regard%20to%20its%20title%2C%20right%2C%20or%20interest%20in%20the%20subject%20land%20in%20question%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20proof%20on%20record%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20question%20having%20any%20historical%20significance%2C%20the%20bench%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20document%20worth%20its%20salt%20on%20the%20record%20that%20the%20temple%20in%20question%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20public%20and%20not%20a%20private%20temple%20managed%20by%20the%20petitioner%20society%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMere%20fact%20that%20the%20prayers%20are%20offered%20at%20the%20temple%20every%20day%20and%20for%20that%20matter%20there%20are%20special%20events%20on%20certain%20festive%20occasions%20does%20not%20convert%20the%20temple%20in%20question%20to%20a%20place%20of%20public%20significance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20the%20foregoing%20discussion%2C%20the%20present%20writ%20petition%20is%20dismissed%2C%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20however%20granted%20the%20petitioner%20society%2015%20days%20time%20to%20remove%20the%20idols%20and%20other%20religious%20objects%20in%20the%20temple%20and%20to%20place%20the%20same%20in%20some%20other%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20fail%20to%20do%20so%2C%20the%20respondent%20DDA%20is%20directed%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20idols%20are%20placed%20in%20some%20other%20temple%2C%20or%20as%20may%20be%20directed%20by%20the%20Religious%20Committee%20if%20they%20are%20approached%20for%20any%20suggestions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20directed%2C%20%26quot%3BLastly%2C%20the%20DDA%20shall%20be%20at%20liberty%20to%20carry%20out%20demolition%20of%20the%20unauthorised%20construction%2C%20and%20the%20petitioner%20society%20and%20its%20members%20shall%20not%20cause%20any%20impediment%20or%20obstacles%20in%20such%20a%20demolition%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20police%20and%20the%20administration%20shall%20render%20full%20assistance%20in%20the%20said%20process%20in%20order%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20directed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717067700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Ft72t3c1g_delhi-high-court-650_6