d%20Northeast%20Together.%20Last%20Time%20Was%20In...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECyclone%20Remal%2C%20which%20formed%20in%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%2C%20has%20led%20to%20India%20witnessing%20a%20rare%20phenomenon%20with%20the%20monsoon%20setting%20in%20simultaneously%20over%20Kerala%20and%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20northeast.%20The%20last%20time%20this%20happened%20was%20in%202017%20and%20there%20was%20one%20factor%20in%20common%20-%20Cyclone%20Mora%20had%20formed%20just%20before%20the%20monsoon%20that%20year%2C%20also%20over%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20Southwest%20Monsoon%20has%20set%20in%20over%20Kerala%20and%20also%20advanced%20into%20most%20of%20northeast%20India%2C%20including%20all%20of%20Nagaland%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Mizoram%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20most%20parts%20of%20Tripura%2C%20Meghalaya%20and%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20usually%20arrives%20in%20Kerala%20on%20June%201%20and%20in%20the%20northeast%20on%20June%205.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20had%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20conditions%20were%20rapidly%20becoming%20favourable%20for%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20southwest%20monsoon%20over%20Kerala%20within%20the%20next%2024%20hours.%20It%20has%20set%20in%20on%20May%2030%2C%20a%20day%20earlier%20than%20the%20weather%20bureau's%20first%20forecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20IMD%20Director%20General%20M%20Mohapatra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20of%20today%2C%20the%20southwest%20monsoon%20has%20reached%20Kerala%20and%20covered%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%20It%20has%20also%20covered%20some%20parts%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20also%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20northeastern%20states.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F