0rates%20to%20ease.%20Check%20out%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-heloc-lenders%5C%22%3Ebest%20HELOC%20lenders%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20start%20your%20search%20for%20the%20right%20loan%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20HELOC%20is%20a%20line%20of%20credit%20that%20lets%20you%20borrow%20against%20the%20equity%20in%20your%20home.%20It%20works%20similarly%20to%20a%20credit%20card%20in%20that%20you%20borrow%20what%20you%20need%20rather%20than%20getting%20the%20full%20amount%20you're%20borrowing%20in%20a%20lump%20sum.%20It%20also%20lets%20you%20tap%20into%20the%20money%20you%20have%20in%20your%20home%20without%20replacing%20your%20entire%20mortgage%2C%20like%20you'd%20do%20with%20a%20cash-out%20refinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22e3f3577dfe678e19f8dce895f3061b13%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcurrent-heloc-rates%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22e3f3577dfe678e19f8dce895f3061b13%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcurrent-heloc-rates%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3ECurrent%20HELOC%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0are%20relatively%20low%20compared%20to%20other%20loan%20options%2C%20including%20credit%20cards%20and%20personal%20loans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhen%20Will%20House%20Prices%20Come%20Down%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20aren't%20likely%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhome-prices-drop%5C%22%3Ehome%20prices%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E%20anytime%20soon%20thanks%20to%20extremely%20limited%20supply.%20In%20fact%2C%20they'll%20likely%20rise%20this%20year%20as%20mortgage%20rates%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%