your%20budget%20could%20handle%20a%20higher%20monthly%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFixed-rate%20mortgage%20are%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20borrowers%20who%20want%20stability%2C%20since%20your%20monthly%20principal%20and%20interest%20payments%20won't%20change%20throughout%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan%20(though%20your%20mortgage%20payment%20could%20increase%20if%20your%20taxes%20or%20insurance%20go%20up).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20exchange%20for%20this%20stability%2C%20you'll%20take%20on%20a%20higher%20rate.%20This%20might%20seem%20like%20a%20bad%20deal%20right%20now%2C%20but%20if%20rates%20increase%20further%20down%20the%20road%2C%20you%20might%20be%20glad%20to%20have%20a%20rate%20locked%20in.%20And%20if%20rates%20trend%20down%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20refinance%20to%20snag%20a%20lower%20rate%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20Does%20an%20Adjustable-Rate%20Mortgage%20Work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fadjustable-rate-mortgage%5C%22%3EAdjustable-rate%20mortgages%3C%2Fa%3E%20start%20with%20an%20introductory%20period%20where%20your%20rate%20will%20remain%20fixed%20for%20a%20certain%20period%20of%20time.%20Once%20that%20period%20is%20up%2C%20it%20will%20begin%20to%20adjust%20periodically%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20once%20per%20year%20or%20once%20every%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20your%20rate%20will%20change%20depends%20on%20the%20index%20that%20the%20ARM%20uses%20and%20the%20margin%20set%20by%20the%20lender.%20Lenders%20choose%20the%20index%20that%20their%20ARMs%20use%2C%20and%20this%20rate%20can%20trend%20up%20or%20down%20depending%20on%20current%20market%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20margin%20is%20the%20amount%20of%20interest%20a%20lender%20charges%20on%20top%20of%20the%20index.%20You%20should%20shop%20around%20with%20multiple%20lenders%20to%20see%20which%20one%20offers%20the%20lowest%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EARMs%20also%20come%20with%20limits%20on%20how%20much%20they%20can%20change%20and%20how%20high%20they%20can%20go.%20For%20example%2C%20an%20ARM%20might%20be%20limited%20to%20a%202%25%20increase%20or%20decrease%20every%20time%20it%20adjusts%2C%20with%20a%20maximum%20rate%20of%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-thursday-30-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717063201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658466f21c5c7b8c9a0b157f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-thursday-30-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20today's%20mortgage%20and%20refinance%20rates.%20Mortgage%20rates%20are%20up%20slightly%20this%20week%2C%20but%20they're%20still%20down%20compared%20to%20where%20they%20were%20a%20month%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Molly%20Grace)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-thursday-30-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blondie%E2%80%99s%20Debbie%20Harry%20Is%20a%20Superstitious%20Aunt%20in%20Trailer%20for%20Tribeca%20Short%20Film%20%E2%80%98Catharsis%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717063200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FCATHARSIS_JOJO_LAM_3.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236019537%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Debbie%20Harry%2C%20lead%20vocalist%20of%20the%20band%20Blondie%2C%20headlines%20the%20cast%20of%20the%20Tribeca-selected%20short%20%E2%80%9CCatharsis.%E2%80%9D%20Brian%20Logvinsky%E2%80%99s%20directorial%20debut%20follows%20a%20dancer%20savant%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20self-destruction%2C%20confronted%20by%20a%20peculiar%20psychotherapist%2