sition%20of%20the%20demonetisation%20disaster%2C%20a%20flawed%20GST%20(goods%20and%20service%20tax)%2C%20and%20the%20painful%20mismanagement%20during%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20miserable%20situation%2C%20where%20an%20expectation%20of%20subpar%20six%20to%20seven%20per%20cent%20GDP%20growth%20has%20become%20the%20new%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAverage%20GDP%20growth%20under%20BJP%20government%20has%20plunged%20to%20under%20six%20per%20cent...%20during%20Congress-UPA%20tenure%20it%20was%20about%20eight%20per%20cent%20(New%20Series).%20Unprecedented%20unemployment%20and%20unbridled%20inflation%20have%20greatly%20widened%20inequality%2C%20which%20is%20now%20at%20a%20100-year%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20World%20Bank%20data%20GDP%20growth%20under%20the%20UPA%20government%20touched%20a%20high%20of%208.5%20per%20cent%20in%202010%2C%20and%20hit%20a%20low%20of%203.1%20per%20cent%20in%202008%20(during%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis).%20In%20the%2010%20years%20since%20it%20has%20reached%20a%20high%20of%209.1%20per%20cent%20(in%202021)%20and%20plummeted%20to%20-5.8%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-black-paper-news-bjp-white-paper-price-rise-unemployment-congress-black-paper-attack-on-government-5019669%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPrice%20Rise%2C%20Joblessnes...%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress'%20Black%20Paper%20On%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20Dr%20Singh's%20letter%20was%20shared%20on%20X%20by%20the%20Congress%20an%20hour%20after%20the%20central%20bank%20released%20its%20annual%20report%2C%20in%20which%20it%20forecast%20real%20GDP%20growth%20of%20seven%20per%20cent%20for%20FY2024%2F25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20a%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20report%20pegged%20overall%20FY2023%2F24%20growth%20at%20eight%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%20said%20the%20UPA%20%26quot%3Bdespite%20challenges%2C%20had%20increased%20purchasing%20power%20of%20our%20people%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20%26quot%3BBJP%20misrule%20has%20resulted%20in%20depletion%20of%20household%20savings%20to%20historic%2047-year%20low%26quot%3B%3B%20in%20FY2022%2F23%20households'%20net%20financial%20savings%20plunged%20to%20a%20five-year%20low%20of%20Rs%2014.2%20trillion%205.3%20per%20cent%20of%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20between%20FY2011%2F12%20and%20FY2021%2F22%20(except%20for%20the%20pandemic%20years)%20the%20same%20figure%20was%20between%20seven%20and%20eight%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDr%20Singh%20On%20Farmers'%20Protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Ffarmers-protest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarmers'%20protests%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20still%20haunt%20the%20centre%20-%20four%20years%20after%20a%20nation-wide%20agitation%20by%20lakhs%20of%20agriculturists%20made%20headlines%20worldwide%2C%20and%20forced%20the%20BJP%20to%20roll%20back%20three%20controversial%20laws%20-%20he%20reproached%20the%20government%20for%20having%20%26quot%3Bleft%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20castigating%20Punjabis%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20if%20the%20lathis%20and%20rubber%20bullets%20were%20not%20enough%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20verbally%20assaulted%20our%20farmers%20by%20calling%20them%20'parasites'%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-resolve-to-intensify-protest-continue-it-during-lok-sabha-polls-5240195%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarmers%20Resolve%20To%20Intensify%20Protest%2C%20Continue%20During%20Polls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20promised%20to%20double%20the%20income%20of%20our%20farmers%20by%202022%20(but)%20his%20policies%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20have%20eroded%20the%20earnings...%20the%20national%20average%20monthly%20income%20of%20farmers%20is%20a%20meagre%20Rs%2027%20per%20day%2C%20while%20average%20debt%20per%20farmer%20is%20Rs%2027%2C000%20(from%20government%20data)%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftear-gas-fired-at-farmers-marching-towards-delhi-at-punjab-haryana-border-5048511%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarmers%20Try%20To%20Cross%20Punjab-Haryana%20Border%2C%20Tear%20Gas%20Used%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20PM%20then%20highlighted%20the%20UPA%20government's%20loan%20waivers%20%26quot%3Bworth%20Rs%2072%2C000%20crore%20to%203.73%20crore%20farmers%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bincreased%20MSP%20(minimum%20support%20price%2C%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20renewed%20farmers%20protest%20against%20the%20BJP%20government)%2C%20and%20increased%20production%2C%20while%20encouraging%20exports%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20today%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20had%20promised%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20MSP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20protesting%20farmers'%20biggest%20demands%2C%20and%20a%20stable%20import-export%20policy%20for%20agriculture%2C%20as%20well%20as%20loan%20waivers%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20transfer%20of%20insured%20compensation%20in%2030%20days%20in%20case%20of%20crop%20loss%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDr%20Singh%20On%20Income%20Disparity%2C%20Jobs%20For%20Youth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%20also%20flagged%20wage%20disparity%20that%20has%20led%20to%20%26quot%3Bwidespread%20distress%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20red-flag%20on%20this%20subject%20comes%20after%20a%20report%20by%20the%20World%20Inequality%20Lab%20in%20March%2C%20which%20