ave%20over%20the%20last%20two%20weeks.%20While%20Mungeshpur%2C%20on%20the%20city's%20northwestern%20fringes%2C%20saw%20the%20mercury%20touching%2052.9%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20a%20person%20died%20in%20a%20city%20hospital%20due%20to%20heatstroke.%20The%20intense%20heat%20has%20sparked%20health%20concerns%2C%20including%20that%20of%20direct%20exposure%20to%20the%20sun's%20rays%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20an%20eye%20stroke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20an%20eye%20stroke%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEye%20stroke%20occurs%20from%20a%20lack%20of%20sufficient%20blood%20flow%20to%20the%20tissues%20located%20in%20the%20front%20part%20of%20the%20optic%20nerve%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pennmedicine.org%2Ffor-patients-and-visitors%2Fpatient-information%2Fconditions-treated-a-to-z%2Feye-stroke%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRisk%2520Factors%2520of%2520Eye%2520Stroke%2Crisk%2520for%2520developing%2520the%2520disease.%5C%22%3EPenn%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Also%20called%20anterior%20ischemic%20optic%20neuropathy%2C%20eye%20stroke%20is%20a%20dangerous%20and%20potentially%20debilitating%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20If%20the%20blockage%20occurs%20as%20the%20blood%20vessels%20emerge%20out%20of%20the%20optic%20nerve%20and%20onto%20the%20retina%2C%20it%20is%20called%20a%20central%20or%20branch%20retinal%20artery%20occlusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20eye%20stroke%20can%20cause%20sudden%20loss%20of%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EImpact%20of%20heat%20on%20eye%20health%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeatwaves%20can%20negatively%20impact%20your%20overall%20eye%20health%20by%20causing%20dehydration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20results%20in%20dry%20eyes%20and%20irritation.%20If%20there%20is%20an%20increase%20in%20exposure%20to%20harmful%20ultraviolet%20(UV)%20rays%2C%20it%20can%20damage%20the%20eyes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20this%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20conditions%20like%20cataracts%2C%20and%20macular%20degeneration%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20high%20temperatures%20can%20aggravate%20allergies.%20More%20frequent%20eye%20rubbing%20can%20introduce%20infections%20or%20cause%20further%20irritation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ESymptoms%20of%20eye%20stroke%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pennmedicine.org%2Ffor-patients-and-visitors%2Fpatient-information%2Fconditions-treated-a-to-z%2Feye-stroke%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRisk%2520Factors%2520of%2520Eye%2520Stroke%2Crisk%2520for%2520developing%2520the%2520disease.%5C%22%3Emajor%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20eye%20stroke%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDryness%20in%20eyes%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConstant%20irritation%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBlurry%20vision%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConjunctivitis%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwelling%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESudden%20vision%20loss%20in%20one%20eye%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELoss%20of%20visual%20contrast%20or%20light%20sensitivity%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ETips%20to%20stay%20safe%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWear%C2%A0sunglasses%20to%20protect%20your%20eyes%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fkeep-your-eyes-safe-by-following-these-tips-during-heatwaves-5770136%5C%22%3Eharmful%20UV%20rays%20causing%20cataracts%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20macular%20degeneration%2C%20and%20other%20eye%20damage.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStay%20hydrated%20to%20avoid%20health%20issues%20related%20to%20heatwaves.%20Drink%20at%20least%20eight%20glasses%20of%20water%20every%20day%2C%20and%20more%20if%20you%20spend%20time%20in%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUV-blocking%20contact%20lenses%20provide%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20protection%20against%20UV%20rays.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEating%20eye-healthy%20food%20with%20nutrients%20like%20omega-3%20fatty%20acids%2C%20vitamins%20C%20and%20E%2C%20and%20zinc%20can%20support%20overall