said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20purportedly%20showing%20the%20soldiers%20storming%20inside%20the%20police%20station%20late%20Tuesday%20evening%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20has%20denied%20assaulting%20the%20cops%20and%20termed%20it%20an%20incident%20of%20%26quot%3Bminor%20differences%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reports%20of%20altercation%20between%20police%20and%20army%20personnel%20and%20beating%20of%20police%20personnel%20are%20mis-founded%20and%20incorrect.%20Minor%20differences%20between%20the%20police%20personnel%20and%20a%20territorial%20army%20unit%20on%20an%20operational%20matter%20have%20been%20amicably%20resolved%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20defence%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20FIR%2C%20police%20have%20named%2016%20soldiers%2C%20including%20three%20officers%20holding%20the%20rank%20of%20Lt%20Colonel.%20They%20have%20been%20booked%20on%20charges%20of%20rioting%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20and%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20policemen%20at%20the%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20cops%20raided%20the%20house%20of%20a%20territorial%20army%20soldier%20at%20Batpora%20village%20in%20Kupwara%20as%20part%20of%20their%20probe%20into%20a%20case%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%20Later%20around%209%3A40%20pm%2C%20the%20army%20soldiers%20swooped%20down%20on%20the%20police%20station%20and%20attacked%20them%2C%C2%A0said%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20number%20of%20armed%20and%20uniformed%20personnel%20of%20160%20Territorial%20Army%2C%20led%20by%20the%20three%20officers%2C%20unauthorisedly%20entered%20the%20police%20station%2C%20it%20said.%20The%20FIR%20said%20the%20troops%2C%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20any%20provocation%2C%20severely%20attacked%20the%20staff%20and%20officers%20present%20at%20the%20police%20station%20with%20rifle%20butts%2C%20kicks%20and%20sticks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20information