ever%2C%20the%20water%20they%20got%20was%20often%20salty%20and%20unclean%20which%20needed%20to%20be%20boiled%20several%20times%20before%20being%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20left%20him%20spending%20days%20in%20search%20of%20solutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wondered%20about%20what%20we%20could%20do.%20Since%20water%20is%20a%20finite%20resource%2C%20how%20could%20we%20make%20its%20usage%20more%20circular%3F%E2%80%9D%20Prashant%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20the%2050-year-old%20found%20was%20using%20greywater%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20domestic%20wastewater%20from%20wash%20basins%2C%20washing%20machines%2C%20showers%2C%20kitchens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20DowntoEarth%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fwater%2Fworld-water-week-2023-reuse-of-greywater-can-be-an-answer-to-india-s-shortage-problem-91223%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520India%252C%2520it%2520is%2520estimated%2Cof%2520the%2520pollutants%2520in%2520each.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3Eestimates%20that%20India%20generates%20about%2031%20billion%20litres%20of%20greywater%20everyday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sustainability%20enthusiast%20found%20that%20recycling%20greywater%20in%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20homes%20could%20be%20a%20viable%20solution%20that%20could%20help%20us%20tide%20over%20the%20water%20crisis%20in%20the%20future.%20This%20recycled%20greywater%20can%20be%20used%20to%20recharge%20groundwater%2C%20water%20plants%2C%20clean%2C%20in%20landscaping%20and%20gardening%2C%20in%20the%20toilet%20flush%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FIMG-20231120-WA0044-min-1716894257.jpg%5C%22%20