However%2C%20websites%20that%20the%20courts%20accept%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20accessibility%20built%20into%20them.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Anchal%20often%20has%20to%20rely%20on%20someone%20else%20to%20help%20her%20navigate%20through%20these%20websites.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20Anchal%20mentions%20how%20even%20the%20IT%20staff%20is%20not%20fully%20aware%20of%20how%20a%20screen%20reader%20works%20and%20how%20it%20can%20be%20amalgamated%20with%20the%20softwares%20used%20at%20the%20workplace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnchal%E2%80%99s%20journey%20underscores%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20widespread%20accessibility%20awareness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disability%20Act%2C%202016%20mandates%20all%20institutions%20and%20workplaces%20to%20provide%20reasonable%20accommodation%20and%20accessible%20infrastructure.%20This%20includes%20offering%20accessible%20materials%20and%20resources%20and%20conducting%20regular%20accessibility%20audits%20to%20identify%20and%20address%20infrastructural%20barriers%20and%20providing%20training%20and%20support%20to%20employees%20with%20disabilities%2C%20along%20with%20conducting%20sensitisation%20programmes%20for%20other%20employees%20and%20people%20in%20the%20workplace%20or%20institution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaw%20is%20a%20competitive%20and%20demanding%20profession%20which%20requires%20one%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20reading%20and%20documentation.%20The%20general%20understanding%20so%20far%20has%20been%20that%20this%20would%20not%20be%20appropriate%20for%20a%20visually-impaired%20person.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20digital%20innovations%20have%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20to%20add%20to%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20profession.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201021px)%20100vw%2C%201021px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%