0to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20over%2072%20outlets%20that%20sell%20over%2020%2C000%20pizzas%20every%20day%2C%20with%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2015%20crore%20in%20the%20last%20financial%20year%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20this%2032-year-old%20went%20from%20having%20arrears%20in%20his%20engineering%20course%20to%20being%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%2C%20providing%20employment%20to%20over%20700%20people!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIntroducing%20a%20city%20to%20the%20taste%20of%20pizza%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20in%20Gohana%20where%20his%20father%20managed%20a%20construction%20material%20business%20%E2%80%94%20a%20setting%20that%20ignited%20his%20early%20entrepreneurial%20spirit.%20Following%20his%20schooling%2C%20he%20studied%20at%20NC%20College%20of%20Engineering%20in%20the%20nearby%20town%20of%20Israna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC61mMzitPC6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC61mMzitPC6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3